    "description": "If you're a passionate Financial Analyst with drive and ambition, BSR & Co Consulting Pvt Ltd in Dhanbad is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout BSR & Co Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nBSR & Co Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n• Maintain general ledger and ensure accurate bookkeeping\n• Liaise with banks, regulators, and financial institutions\n• Prepare annual reports and investor presentations\n• Process payroll and manage employee reimbursements\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Python for Finance\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in Income Tax\n• Proficiency in Forecasting\n• Proficiency in Bloomberg Terminal\n• Proficiency in VBA\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in SQL\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Learning & development budget\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Flexible working hours\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Dhanbad, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with BSR & Co Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
